34:49.918 --> 34:51.533
and there's two people
in this firehouse

34:51.568 --> 34:52.632
that are doing something

34:52.667 --> 34:55.533
they both know
they shouldn't be doing.

34:55.568 --> 34:59.532
That goddamn prick.
He told you?

34:59.567 --> 35:01.667
I will kick his ass,
that little piece of shit.

35:01.702 --> 35:03.767
Couldn't keep his mouth shut
for one goddamn day...

35:03.802 --> 35:05.001
Any guesses on that?

35:05.036 --> 35:06.234
Just one.

35:14.201 --> 35:15.498
What are you doin' here?

35:15.533 --> 35:17.183
I said
I needed to talk to you.

35:17.218 --> 35:18.834
But why didn't you just call me?

35:18.869 --> 35:20.233
What's your problem?

35:20.268 --> 35:21.765
Because if these guys get wind

35:21.800 --> 35:23.199
of what's going on
between us, anything,

35:23.234 --> 35:25.500
it's gonna be the shit storm
to end all shit storms.

35:25.535 --> 35:26.533
Okay? You gotta be careful.

35:26.568 --> 35:27.584
Oh, I'm very careful.

35:27.619 --> 35:28.565
Oh, yeah. Bullshit.

35:28.600 --> 35:30.400
Name one time when
I have not been careful.

35:30.435 --> 35:31.699
My mom's wake.

35:31.734 --> 35:33.533
Okay, you practically mauled me
next to the coffin.

35:33.568 --> 35:35.333
- I did not.
- Yes, you did.

35:35.368 --> 35:37.767
Mickey talked to me about it.
Janet talked to me about it.

35:37.802 --> 35:39.801
Well, anyways, I still
need to talk to you.

35:39.836 --> 35:41.634
All right, well,
I'll come over tonight.

35:41.669 --> 35:43.433
- Come on. You gotta go.
- Do you promise?

35:43.468 --> 35:44.567
Yes, I promise you, okay?

35:44.602 --> 35:46.101
- Ow, ow, ow!
- What?

35:46.136 --> 35:47.368
You're hurting me!

35:47.403 --> 35:48.768
I kinda like it.

35:48.803 --> 35:50.134
Stop. Jesus Christ.

35:52.967 --> 35:54.734
Hey, Laura, listen.
Tonight--

35:54.769 --> 35:56.398
- Um, I was--
- You asshole!

35:56.433 --> 35:58.767
You couldn't keep
your mouth shut for one day?

35:58.802 --> 36:00.567
One day?
I knew this was a mistake.

36:00.602 --> 36:01.765
- I knew it.
- Wait a second--

36:01.800 --> 36:03.883
And when you see me,
don't even look at me.

36:03.918 --> 36:05.967
Don't talk to me.
Don't say my name. Nothing.

36:08.567 --> 36:09.567
Not your day, kid.

36:09.602 --> 36:11.234
Not your day.

36:18.700 --> 36:20.166
Hey, what are you
still doing here?

36:20.201 --> 36:21.800
I thought you were
taking Jeannie to dinner

36:21.835 --> 36:22.765
before the show.

36:22.800 --> 36:23.932
Yeah, I thought so too.

36:23.967 --> 36:26.301
The stupid show starts
in about an hour.

36:26.336 --> 36:27.934
I don't know where
the hell she is.

36:27.969 --> 36:29.585
Hey, chief. Phone.

36:29.620 --> 36:30.994
Maybe that's her now.

36:31.029 --> 36:32.368
All right, good luck.

36:34.400 --> 36:35.498
Yeah.

36:35.533 --> 36:36.900
Yeah, is this
Jerry Reilly?

36:36.935 --> 36:38.233
Yeah, this is Jerry Reilly.

36:38.268 --> 36:41.867
Jerry, Dave Weidman
from 72 Truck downtown.

36:41.902 --> 36:43.066
Dave. What do you got?

36:43.101 --> 36:46.600
Well, actually, um,
I've got your wife here.

36:46.635 --> 36:48.166
What?

36:48.201 --> 36:50.067
I think she's lost.

36:52.400 --> 36:54.416
Where you at?
I'll be right there.

36:54.451 --> 36:56.542
My shift's over.
I'm heading uptown.

36:56.577 --> 36:58.634
If you want,
I could bring her to you.

36:58.669 --> 36:59.634
Yeah,
I appreciate that.

36:59.669 --> 37:01.268
Thanks, Dave.

37:06.167 --> 37:07.132
Well.

37:07.167 --> 37:08.301
How was your day, sunshine?

37:08.336 --> 37:09.999
Oh, just great.

37:10.034 --> 37:13.400
Full of self-hatred and misery
and blackness,

37:13.435 --> 37:15.134
just like every other day.

37:15.169 --> 37:16.799
What are
you guys doing?

37:16.834 --> 37:18.433
Arlo's teaching me
how to play chess.

37:20.467 --> 37:22.533
That piece can't attack
that way, Teddy.

37:22.568 --> 37:24.565
I got news for you, pal.
It just did.

37:24.600 --> 37:27.301
Hey, check out the envelope
on the counter.

37:27.336 --> 37:28.735
4800 on the dot.

37:28.770 --> 37:30.099
- Really?
- Yeah.

37:30.134 --> 37:31.932
Arlo was on fire
today.

37:31.967 --> 37:33.565
We get to go
into the saddling ring.

37:33.600 --> 37:35.600
Arlo gets to stare the horses
square in the face.

37:35.635 --> 37:37.632
Bingo! We cleaned up.

37:37.667 --> 37:39.134
You can thank me now,
ass-face.

37:40.700 --> 37:41.634
Yeah, maybe later.

37:42.834 --> 37:44.234
Hey, where's my old man?

37:44.269 --> 37:45.968
Uh, gone.

37:46.003 --> 37:47.632
Check.

37:47.667 --> 37:49.500
That's not check,
dipshit.

37:49.535 --> 37:50.699
Gone where?

37:50.734 --> 37:52.800
- Ireland.
- He went to Ireland?

37:52.835 --> 37:53.932
Yeah, Ireland.

37:53.967 --> 37:56.600
Yeah, he said something
about you pissing him off.

37:56.635 --> 37:59.234
Wait, he just packed his bags
and went to Ireland?

37:59.269 --> 38:00.199
Checkmate.

38:00.234 --> 38:02.665
Jesus Christ,
I give up.

38:02.700 --> 38:05.433
Did he say
when he was comin' back?

38:05.468 --> 38:07.832
Nah.

38:07.867 --> 38:10.032
Hey, Tom,
it's not just you.

38:10.067 --> 38:11.934
Your father's only been
to Ireland once,

38:11.969 --> 38:13.299
back after the war.

38:13.334 --> 38:15.368
He just wanted to see it again
before he died.

38:15.403 --> 38:19.034
He's gonna be
okay, Tom.

38:19.069 --> 38:21.268
He's gonna be fine.

38:25.400 --> 38:27.167
Taxi!

38:29.767 --> 38:31.717
What the hell
happened, Jeannie?

38:31.752 --> 38:33.743
I don't like to drive
in the city.

38:33.778 --> 38:35.734
- I got confused.
- I'm confused too.

38:35.769 --> 38:37.333
This show with puppets and--

38:37.368 --> 38:39.767
Here, let me find the tickets.
You know we're 10 minutes late.

38:39.802 --> 38:40.799
I'm sorry!

38:40.834 --> 38:41.967
That's okay. I'm thrilled.

38:42.002 --> 38:42.999
Let's go.

38:43.034 --> 38:44.433
Okay, but when
my husband gets here,

38:44.468 --> 38:45.834
you have to give him
your seat.

38:45.869 --> 38:47.299
What?

38:47.334 --> 38:50.001
You'll have to give him
your seat. Let's go inside.

38:58.901 --> 39:00.368
Oh, God.

39:04.201 --> 39:06.101
You okay, sweetie?

39:06.136 --> 39:08.432
Yeah.

39:08.467 --> 39:11.101
You're being quiet
tonight.

39:11.136 --> 39:12.734
Just thinking.

39:12.769 --> 39:13.767
About?

39:15.667 --> 39:18.467
Nothing.

39:21.867 --> 39:23.301
You know...

39:24.867 --> 39:27.799
Maybe...

39:27.834 --> 39:30.817
Maybe you're right,
what you said before.

39:30.852 --> 39:33.800
You know, about us
moving in together.

39:33.835 --> 39:36.617
Maybe we should wait,
you know?

39:36.652 --> 39:39.400
Get to know
one another better.

39:41.167 --> 39:42.467
Right?

39:43.901 --> 39:46.034
I thought, um...

39:49.467 --> 39:52.533
Is it the bulimia...
that's scaring you?

39:55.067 --> 39:56.834
Yeah, that's part of it.

39:58.334 --> 40:00.067
What's the other part?

40:04.767 --> 40:07.001
I'm kinda tired.

40:15.567 --> 40:16.767
Hey.

40:18.368 --> 40:20.084
You-know-who is asleep.

40:20.119 --> 40:21.765
- Finally.
- Yeah, finally.

40:21.800 --> 40:23.783
Now we can have
some fun, huh?

40:23.818 --> 40:25.767
Yeah, I can't have
the kind of fun

40:25.802 --> 40:26.799
that I wanna have

40:26.834 --> 40:30.301
with a little girl
sleeping in the next room.

40:30.336 --> 40:32.365
You gotta decide.

40:32.400 --> 40:35.134
Are you gonna be her daddy,
or you gonna be my daddy?

40:37.134 --> 40:39.533
China, is this a decision
that we have to make right now?

40:39.568 --> 40:43.001
Can't it wait, say,
you know, 20 minutes?

40:43.036 --> 40:46.001
Uh, no.
No, it can't.

40:50.067 --> 40:51.400
Come in.

40:55.467 --> 40:56.901
There you go.

40:57.967 --> 40:59.533
Thank you.

41:16.001 --> 41:17.400
Uruguay.

43:00.513 --> 43:02.483
Glad you could find
the time.

